<C>__{susan}
<P>__{(to emt)}
<D>__{where'd you find it?}
<C>__{emt}
<D>__{washed up at the filtration plant on bank street. some asshole there thought it was a baby. they called us.}
<A>__{susan bends over it. she covers her mouth and nose at the stench.}
