<D>__{it's a lobster, right?}
<A>__{but it's not. what lies on the stretcher before them looks more like a demon from a brueghel painting. a three foot insect. it's mephitic, pink white body is rotten, falling apart. the head's intact, with strange, large jaws thrown wide open. the chitin on one is half gone.}
